Golem is framework developed for Python, in order to teach the basics of programming and algorithms and to develop 2D
games.
Golem is open-source project.

One part of the program will run on a Web server and access to it will be using a Web browser. The second part will be
issued as a supplement for Python.

Requieres
=========
- Python 2.6
- Babel
- PyGame, SDL libraries
- C compiler (gcc)


How to…
========

installation PyGame to Gentoo:
>> su -c 'USE="jpeg png" emerge pygame"

compile C source codes:
>> python setup.py build_ext --inplace

	- on Windows® you must often specify compilator with option: --compiler=mingw32
